Several of the songs you've listed as "never officially released" were actually officially released. The two solo versions of "Defying Gravity" were released as iTunes singles IIRC and "I Wanna Sex You Up", "I Could Have Danced All Night" and "Leaving on a Jet Plane" were released as tracks 18-20 on the Target Exclusive version of "Glee: The Music, Volume 1".
